  Siok8 ti7 Hi-liap8 kok u7 chit8-e5 sio2 pang-kok, mia5-cho3 Lo5-kiat; sou2-chai7 khah- phiah, kin7-oa2 soaN-kha. Kok-lai7 im5-loan7 e5 hong-siok8 chin seng7, Kok-ong5 put-chi2 thong3-hin7--in; chiu7 siat giam5-kin2 e5 kim3-leng7, lai5 thong-ti hiah-e5 peh-seN3 kong2, na7-u7 lang5 hoan7-tioh8 im5-loan7 e5 choe7 beh phah in nng7-lui2 bak8-chiu, bo5 beh sia3--i. Kok-ong5 u7 chit8-e5 Thai3-chu2, bin7-mau7 si3-pan, hou7-tiong7, seng-seng5 put- siok8; lang5 long2 ng3-bang7 i e7 seng5 tai7-khi3 lai5 chiap-ui7. Ti7 chit8-jit8 Thai3-chu2 hut-jian5 hoan7-tioh8 chit e5 kim3-leng7. hou7 lang5 ka7 i chhut-phoa3; chha5-kho2 hit-e5-su7 ko2-chin u7-iaN2. Kok-ong5 chek-si5 beh chiau3 kok-hoat pan7--i; choan2-siuN7 kong2, Goa2 chi2-u7 chit-chit8-tiau5 e5 hiat-meh8, toan3-toan3 m7-thang choat8-liau2 chou2-chong e5 hou7-su5; m7-ku2 kok-hoat iu7 be7-sai2--tit to5-chau2. Na7 in-ui7 su-su7 lai5 hoe3- bo5 kong-gi7, beh an2-choaN2 siat-lip8 hoat-tou7 ? In-ui7 lek8-ai3 lai5 phian-than2, beh an2- choaN2 ka3-si7 peh-seN3? Cha2-am3 chhau-sim peh-pak; ai3-tit liong2-choan5-ki5-bi2, iu7 bo5 hit-e5 ke3. SiuN7-kau3 be7-chiah8 be7-khun3--tit; hut-jian5-kan u7 chit8-jit8 siuN7-chhut the3- siok8 e5 ke3-ti3; chiu7 tng cheng3-lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5, kah i-e5 Thai3-chu2 lai5 kui7--teh, chhiat-chhiat chek-pi7--i, kong2, Goa2 chham li2 lun7 in, si7 pe7-kiaN2, lun7 gi7, si7 kun-sin5; hoat-lut8 sit8-chai7 be7 to5-pi7--tit, chong2-si7 in-cheng5 ia7 oh-tit koah ia7; li2 na7 ko2-jian5 e7 kai2-ko3 oaN7 sin-houh, goa2 goan7 chham li2 tau3-siu7-choe7. Chek-si5 ka- ti7 phah chit8-lui2 bak8-chiu khi2--lai5, kah Heng5-tiong7 ia7 phah in Thai3-chu2 chit8-bak8. Thai3-chu2 siong-sim kau3-kek8 chham2-chheh hoan2-hoe2 chiong5-chian5 e5 sit-chho3, toa7-siaN kong2, Goa2 e5 pe7 cho7-ui7, chiah-ni7 chun, ni5-hoe3, chiah-ni7 lau7, lai5 the3-goa2 siu7-khou2, goa2 sim m7-si7 chha5--e5 chioh8--e5, goa2 beh-thai3-e7 jim2--tit--leh? Chu7 hit-si5 chheng-sim koaN2-iok8, se2-thoa7 tek-heng7, kai2-ko3 oaN7-sin; kau3-boe2 ko2-jian5 cho3