  Khi3-chin-chu2 teh phoe-pheng5 kong2, ThiN-e7 bo5 hit-ho7 m7-thiaN3-kiaN2 e5 pe7; ham7- loh8-choe7, pe7 kap i siu7 heng5-hoat8, kau3 au7-lai5 kiaN2 e7-hiau2-tit hoan2-hoe2 kai2-ko3, hou7 pe7 lai5 tit-tioh8 hian5 e5 kiaN2. lang5 chai hit e5 kiaN2 e7 ke2-piN3 chiong5-chian5 e5 chho3-gou7, kiam2 ia7 soa3 chai si7 tui3 hit-e5 pe7 e5 eng7- sim kau3-hiah-ni7 khou2 lai5--e5 mah? TaN ThiN-pe7 chhong3-cho7 lang5-lui7, khoaN3-cho3 i3-ai3 e5 kiaN2; lang5 ki3-jian5 hoan7 choe7, i na7 chiau3 kong-gi7 eng7 thiN-li2 lai5 chek-hoat8--lan2, m7-ku2 hai7-tioh8 in-cheng5, na7 in-ui7 su- cheng5 it-bi7 lai5 sia3-bian2--lan2, m7-ku2 hai7- tioh8 kong-gi7. Sou2-i2 chiah hoa3-sin kang3- loh8 se3-kan, mia5-cho3 Ia5-sou, lai5 the3-lang5 siu7-khou2, kiu3 chiah-e5 ban7-peh-seN3; lun7 jin5-ai3 ia7 kau3, lun7 kong-gi7 ia7 chin; sit8-chai7 si7 chin bo5-ta7-oa5 e5 khou2-sim. KhoaN3 Lo5-ma2 3:26. Lang5 siat-su2 e7 hiau2-tit se2- tu5 oaN7-sin, i2-keng po3 i-e5 toa7-in, ban7-hun7 ia7 po3 bo5 chit8-hun7. Hit-ho7 kian7-koai put- siu7 kau3-hoa3--e5 chong2 be7-bian2--tit tioh8 hou7 I khian3-chek. Che m7-si7 ThiN-pe7 khi3- choat8 lang5, sit8-chai7 si7 lang5 ka-ti7 khi3- choat8 lah!
  (Tai5-lam5-hu2-siaN5 kau3-hoe7-po3 te7 17 tiuN, 1886 ni5 11 goeh8)
